{"tid":2105372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭又帶頭犯法 口罩注意事項冇中英對照","createTime":"2020-07-12T15:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T15:30:32.000Z","uid":300946,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a460adfb0c7bfaf3f4c327c586a0928d45061352","tid":2105372,"uid":300946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"《消費品安全規例》（第456A章）於1998年4月實施。該規例訂明任何有關於消費品的存放、使用、耗用或處置的警告字句必須以<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">中文及英文</span></span>表達。該警告亦須是清楚易讀的，並須放置於消費品的顯眼處、在其包裝上、或將有關警告標籤穩固地貼於其包裝上，或將有關警告文件放在其包裝內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3c77O21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3c77O21.jpg&h=76c105a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%89%E6%BE%B3%E9%82%A8%E7%88%86%E7%96%AB-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E5%90%91%E6%AF%8F%E6%88%B6%E6%B4%BE-50-%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%85%A8%E7%B0%A1%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B3%2589%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2582%25A8%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE-50-%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%25A3%259D%2F&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZosxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=178b090e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B3%2589%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2582%25A8%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE-50-%25E5%2580%258B%2